{"tid":2417631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"夏寶龍強調「最迫切」完善選舉制度 落實行政主導","createTime":"2021-02-22T04:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T05:09:58.000Z","uid":42804,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fa14c7e2e7e7329016c15b2dbad622b7be9bb94e","tid":2417631,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T04:58:42.000Z","msg":"全面管治權︱夏寶龍強調「最迫切」完善選舉制度 落實行政主導 重要法定機關負責人由真正愛國者擔任<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n夏寶龍列舉「愛國者」的多項條件，指歇斯底里攻擊中央、公開宣揚港獨、在國際「唱衰」香港、要求外國制裁、觸犯國安法以及「攬炒派」，都不是愛國者。<br />\n<br />\n夏又指，香港選舉制度不能照搬或套用外國制度，須符合香港實際情況、有利於維護國家安全及保持香港長期繁榮穩定的選舉制度，就是最好的制度。 <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210222/XLSVKZVQ4BBLLFNMQJCDTWJ7CA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210222%2FXLSVKZVQ4BBLLFNMQJCDTWJ7CA%2F&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=1b0b6e51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210222%2FXLSVKZVQ4BBLLFNMQJCDTWJ7CA%2F&h=0b5ce871\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210222/XLSVKZVQ4BBLLFNMQJCDTWJ7CA/</a>"},{"pid":"c9e5285d1926cdcab75b47e2057bad193364fa75","tid":2417631,"uid":80724,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:00:07.000Z","msg":"重選乜鬼啊，直接委任啦屌"},{"pid":"1d90c241c5ad3c99e8040e46cb8e4cba8e1adb6b","tid":2417631,"uid":55955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:02:23.000Z","msg":"DQ晒之後同人講有選舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁習近平都係民選啦"},{"pid":"619c3105276f5914866733daf2c3fe6eff745b2a","tid":2417631,"uid":78039,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"1d90c241c5ad3c99e8040e46cb8e4cba8e1adb6b","tid":2417631,"uid":55955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:02:23.000Z","msg":"DQ晒之後同人講有選舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁習近平都係民選啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:05:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BiO3GhZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBiO3GhZ.jpg&h=d04b82c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14187319503ce3889b2df082a69e480818c2c1d0","tid":2417631,"uid":18477,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:08:13.000Z","msg":"維護維尼安全<br />\n保持香港長期繁榮穩定<br />\n<br />\nok即係又係時候攞返個齒輪出嚟啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ULBSBf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ULBSBf.gif&h=8c9110ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3425d4d0fce608178e842fa9096faa297148349","tid":2417631,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:08:51.000Z","msg":"夏：當年鄧公留下殘缺的選舉制度，今日必要完善起來。"},{"pid":"f4a036900a9c7dafe8e7168b35a77769094702cb","tid":2417631,"uid":34722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:09:58.000Z","msg":"選舉點都有輸既可能，要唔輸就只有直接委任，諗咁多都浪費時間"}]}